ygData.messageBody:
I think I went to Netherbian Lair after PC, and stayed there until they turned light blue, and then went on to The Overthere.  I stayed at the overthere until level 49 or so.  There's always a group to join in that zone.
 
Athiarna Aoibhell, Disciple monk
*Bristlebane*
